    Logistic Regression Function

    log_reg(X, y)

    Arguments

    pred

    X matrix n number rows beta plus 1 number of columns with first column being entirely ones.

    resp

    y vector of length n.

    Value

    A list containing the following attributes:

    betas

    estimated beta coefficients

    y_pred

    predicted y-values using estimated coefficients

    y_actual

    original vector of y-values

    X

    original matrix of predictors
